# mcp-note-ingest

Day 22 MCP server for Markdown vault ingestion.

## What this now supports

This server now supports:

- stdio transport
- `initialize`
- `tools/list`
- `ping`
- `ingest_chat_markdown`

## Main tool

### `ingest_chat_markdown`

This tool writes a new Markdown file into:

```text
Inbox/AI Chats/YYYY/MM/